application.model

Class Flight

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.model.Flight
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataWrapper<Flight>, java.lang.Comparable<Flight>

    public class Flight
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Flight>, DataWrapper<Flight>
    Holds all the information about a single flight, which is uniquely identified by an id. Each flight has a flight number, a date and time, origin, destiny, plane model, company operating the flight, and terminal. Some times, if a plane is operated by more than one company, the flight also includes a list of shared flights, which contain the info about other companies sharing the flight.
